--- Install requirments: ---
  - lowdown
  - pkg-config
  - GNU autotools(automake, autoconf, etc...)

--- Installing lowdown libs ---
You can copy paste the following commands to install lowdown libraries

git clone https://github.com/kristapsdz/lowdown
cd lowdown
./configure
sudo make install_libs

--- Installing coredoc ---
Since lowdown installs its pkg-config file in /usr/local make sure to set you're pkg-config search path
before building like below

export PKG_CONFIG_PATH=/usr/local/lib/pkgconfig

Now build the program like below:

./autogen
./configure
make
sudo make install
